{
  "texts": [
    "From this subset, we manually identified 79 fact-checks that cite congress.gov in the sources and evoke the Vote frame.",
    "For each voting claim, we manually verified the bills referenced within the fact-check are related to the claim to ensure the accuracy of our dataset.",
    "Similarly, we collected 68 fact-checks that cite oecd.org for our analysis of OECD-related claims.",
    "Each OECD claim was manually verified and mapped to the database table which can be used to fact-check it.",
    "Additional details are provided in Appendix A."
  ]
}